{"tid":1999280,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特：勿當信用卡作搖錢樹","createTime":"2020-05-03T05:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T06:42:06.000Z","uid":134993,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a7cf0871feff87a7366ebee21b47a0f7d13104ef","tid":1999280,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"有投資者問及巴菲特如何看信用卡利率不斷上升，以及是否預期未來有回落趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n他認為信用卡利率未來會有很大的機會上升，而他對所有人的建議是不要當信用卡是隨時拿錢的「豬仔錢罌」，因為利率過高。曾有一個女人告訴他出現經濟問題，只能靠信用卡去支撐，但利率高達18%。但若他在同樣情況，他會用所有方法去還款﹐因為巴菲特認為自己都沒有任何投資可以賺取18%的回報。他認為無論如何，人們也不應支付超過12%的利率。"},{"pid":"1a45bcf5d0287ed9a5d5b07627ebd77321d1839d","tid":1999280,"uid":40397,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"香港人太醒<br />\n剩係拎著數，唔會比多利息<br />\n搞到d回贈係越縮越少"},{"pid":"784dc71d651db9501f4ce5dd40832ecf1f10ce1a","tid":1999280,"uid":88896,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:06:09.000Z","msg":"長期擦信用卡cash rebate，知錯了"},{"pid":"471641788a4ef1d75a31513b2e93d9f0500f6218","tid":1999280,"uid":16029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:08:21.000Z","msg":"廢老講廢話"},{"pid":"639cbda1865f21a381f878b597e1849469027eba","tid":1999280,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"471641788a4ef1d75a31513b2e93d9f0500f6218","tid":1999280,"uid":16029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:08:21.000Z","msg":"廢老講廢話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"咁大個陷阱都大把人中伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea50cecfa27761a5d8f2480e9ce965eebfa9904e","tid":1999280,"uid":68556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:13:52.000Z","msg":"長期卡數幾十萬，知錯了。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79771aa88f96b1cde56459f753fec1e7fa550b1c","tid":1999280,"uid":68728,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid